-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1:create a package with npm init command and follow along giving all the details
    install express package and save it to package.json file
    create a file server.js
2:create a public folder and and index.html file
3:write basic codes to test the server using express
4:create a controller folder and include it in the index file
5:write tags to get data from the controller



